oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Military Personnel List, SSU 558 (2)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Military Personnel list that details the men affiliated with the SSU 558. The list also includes information about their military grade, civilian occupation, class, date of recruitment, date of birth, and home address. On the front side of the list Robert F. Hodge appears third from bottom. The list has come apart and is contained within two sleeves.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Robert Frank Hodge World War I Papers, 1914-1919
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: American Field Service; World War, 1914-1918
Military records
